{"tid":1475484,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"運動模式要創新！","createTime":"2019-08-15T13:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:43:58.000Z","uid":293887,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1df0d0eacfc708d05110fa8acdb5f9b5209bdbb","tid":1475484,"uid":293887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"而家既運動模式需要再創新了<br />\n<br />\n首先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既攻勢強左，佢地已經摸熟左抗爭者既心理同戰略，佢地拉人頻率高左好多，長期落去會令士氣大幅動搖，亦令受害既人增加。打快閃係好既戰術，但可唔可以中途加多d新元素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢??<br />\n<br />\n上星期6紅隧快閃，渣車人士免費過隧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係一個好好既運動，搞多幾次一定好受歡迎，甚至令人期待，比我渣車既話，見到你搞都自願讓路比你搞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試唸下：如果大家每次行動，其他人幫返你轉頭，幫手令你地快d成功，咁就更加可以we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &lt;3<br />\n<br />\n突然唸起<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">快相機</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快相機既用途係測速，超過就會影相再傳告票。但大部分相機都係唔合理既位置。例如一段70轉50既指示牌後面好快就有一部機，呢個距離係唔足夠減速，如果睇到指示牌先減速就一定會中招，所以指示不單唔可靠，更會被罰款。好多司機都話第一次行果d路都實中招，並唔係因為危險駕駛，而係比快相機陰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n同過好多渣車人士傾過下計，黃又好藍又好，都話快相機專陰鳩人罰錢。佢地都話快相機而家既位置唔會減少意外發生，只係為罰人而存在。咁超速又真係唔岩啊，所以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千萬唔好用噴油噴黑鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>，希望大家一齊brainstorm下可以點樣愛護快相機鏡頭啦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下apps可以詳細列出全港快相機位置<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobi.coolapps.speedcameraalert.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dmobi.coolapps.speedcameraalert.hk&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=92ec9d09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mobi.coolapps.speedcameraalert.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n不合作運動既核心價值係<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">造福市民，打擊政府</span></ins></strong>，咁樣做不單止爭取更多人支持，更可以壓制政府，逼佢地重新接納民意，最緊要係更安全、更符合be water概念～"},{"pid":"39a6c8e51584ab774d82d1240aeaa61449ab591e","tid":1475484,"uid":34478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"用鐳射槍 射鳩個鏡頭"},{"pid":"e5d55011d435bb9b80af0cc6c270df4151f7ed14","tid":1475484,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經post冇人推！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略</span> </span><br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能好評 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHHFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f724bc6d212f6a6a2274828c4f0fd9a1a26575ca","tid":1475484,"uid":274003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T16:43:58.000Z","msg":"啲快相機條柱咁高，爬唔爬到上去都要考慮喎。"}]}